{
  "stem": "11296.2",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Try not to get beaten from the Germans, from the SS, because when they gonna put-- they're going to start beating you, or you are not working, or you're doing something-- you are lost.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Had to listen.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So me, Hanka, and some other girls right away we became-- all the girls who slept together with us-- became like sisters.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Really it was five-- not all of them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Me and Hanka, and three more.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They were from not far-- they came from all the same ghetto.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we said, you know, whatever somebody is going to have, we're going to share with each other.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And really, we did this, you know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So around everybody in the beginning, nobody-- nobody had a good job, nobody had nothing.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We start learning what's going on then.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we went to work, you know, we went to the quarries.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We went to other work-- like we was making-- we went to the water, and we had to straighten out the lakes.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So the work was really-- the work had nothing for them.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They didn't have nothing, they just-- we went to work just to kill us.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So the next work, it was-- we went on a farm, and there was houses, standing brick houses.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So they gave us, again, the picks, and we had to take down, one by one, the red bricks.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the girls-- the one who took them down-- there was another commander who was cleaning them.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So we didn't understand why they need bricks, you know.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "People was here to take apart the houses.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So from these bricks-- so the people who worked the sonderkomando-- sonderkommando, this was a group of people who worked in the crematoriums.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And then, in the time when we came, they were still building.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
